title: King Me (Chet Pete)
description:
Releasing your control can unlock God’s presence in your life. 

In “King Me,” the Elevation University City Pastor, Chetwyn Pete, reminds us what being in charge looks like when God’s in control.

If you’ve just made a decision for Christ, please respond HERE: http://ele.vc/tIepfr

To support this ministry and help us continue to reach people all around the world click here: http://www.elevationchurch.org/giving/

Scripture References:

Genesis 41, verses 38-44

Deuteronomy 28, verse 13

Genesis 39, verses 2-9
